[name]
ISO-8859-1 encoding with forced UTF-8 output

[options]
utf8 1

[input]
=encoding iso-8859-1

=head1 ACCENTS

Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!!

    Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
      Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
        Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!

Older versions didn't convert Beyoncé in verbatim.

[output]
ACCENTS
    Beyoncé! Beyoncé! Beyoncé!!

        Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
          Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
            Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!

    Older versions didn't convert Beyoncé in verbatim.
